TextBody:
Hello Werner,

We can schedule a remote session for tomorrow and we can inject the new EPP Clients on the EPP Server.
This way, you will be able to download the new EPP Client from the EPP UI and you will be able to choose if you want to include the addons or not in the package.

Best regards,
Emil
